Global MRO Adhesive Market Insights
MRO Adhesive Market size was valued at USD 4.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 6.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.9% from 2024 to 2030.

MRO Adhesive Market Overview
The MRO (Maintenance, Repair, and Overhaul) adhesive market is valued at approximately USD 7.6 billion in 2024 and is projected to grow at a CAGR of 5.4% from 2025 to 2030. The market’s growth is primarily driven by the increasing demand for durable and high-performance adhesive solutions across industries such as aerospace, automotive, construction, and manufacturing. MRO adhesives are essential in repairing and maintaining critical infrastructure and machinery, thereby enhancing operational efficiency. Furthermore, the expanding industrial sectors, especially in emerging economies, are further fueling the demand for MRO adhesives. Increasing advancements in adhesive technologies and their enhanced properties, including heat and chemical resistance, are also contributing to the market's expansion.

